trans-unit.source: Obtains the file locations of Web services discovery documents for use in populating another Web services discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar filplatser för Web services discovery-dokument för användning i fylla i en annan Web services discovery-dokumentet.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern> class and is employed by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> class's <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method, which handles an HTTP request for a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern klassen ärver från abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>klassen och anställda av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler>klassens <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metod som hanterar HTTP-begäran för en discovery-dokumentet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>

trans-unit.source: Normally, none of these classes need to be used directly by a developer.
trans-unit.target: Ingen av dessa klasser behöver normalt användas direkt av en utvecklare.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentSearchPattern"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"></xref> object for a given discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"> </xref> objekt för en given discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The concrete <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> class.
trans-unit.target: Den konkreta <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>klassen ärver från en abstrakt <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference>klass.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> instance contains the location of the .vsdisco file, which is also the file system directory corresponding to the HTTP request passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>instans innehåller platsen för filen .vsdisco, som också är filen systemkatalogen motsvarar HTTP-begäran skickades till den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>

trans-unit.source: The file system path of the discovery document.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"></xref> object that specifies the location of a .vsdisco file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference"> </xref> objekt som anger platsen för en .vsdisco-fil.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file name pattern to use as a search target.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar filnamnsmönster som ska användas som ett mål för sökning.

trans-unit.source: The pattern "*.vsdisco" indicates a .vsdisco Web services discovery document extension.
trans-unit.target: Mönstret "*.vsdisco" anger .vsdisco tillägget Web services discovery för dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern> class, on the other hand, indicates a .disco extension.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern>klass, å andra sidan, anger ett .disco tillägg.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentLinksPattern>
